{"tid":1815144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"仇栩欣：N95口罩已經炒到20蚊1個","createTime":"2020-01-07T09:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T21:29:44.000Z","uid":389,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d47524731dc9a1a8ab9c105bcf23954e66a4bd0","tid":1815144,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"今日會議提到人命攸關的武漢疫情，和富區的工聯會郭偉強竟然認為相關議案「太低級」😅 <br />\n<br />\n正如我在會上的發言，阿欣要求政府公開及透明地處理疫情最新情況，盲目在記者會上唱官腔只會帶來更大的恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n相信保皇黨及其黨羽一定會批評上述議案是嘩眾取寵的政治操作，但在人心惶惶之際，政府不是有必要率隊視察穩定民心嗎？今日的報紙提到，N95 口罩已經炒到$20/一個。證明市民已經陷入恐慌狀態。連資源不多的區議員，也要自掏腰包派口罩安撫民情的時候，何解衛生署卻沒有相關行動呢？<br />\n<br />\n阿欣懇請當局正視問題，不要讓十七年前的悲劇再次重演。一次的傷痛，已經是香港無法回首的深淵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5TLO5R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5TLO5R.png&h=e93a789b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f82937d186eae33ab6f18da298a4d321b022fa01","tid":1815144,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"郭偉強真係人型垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee78d7f34226d358ecb3536cc5890613ad299958","tid":1815144,"uid":78470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"少數派為反而反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7826908376547a06672e2e28f92703dd62f5a03b","tid":1815144,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee78d7f34226d358ecb3536cc5890613ad299958","tid":1815144,"uid":78470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"少數派為反而反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"有破壞無建設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a4ed1c8fd302ef410671ae49161c5f5d25505f","tid":1815144,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f82937d186eae33ab6f18da298a4d321b022fa01","tid":1815144,"